Get MERRA-2 grid

Source: R/locid.R
getGrid.Rd

Get MERRA-2 grid

getGrid(
  type = "points",
  class = "sp",
  locid = NULL,
  lon = c(-180, 180),
  lat = c(-90, 90)
)

Arguments

type

type of grid-data to return, spatial points ("points") or polygons ("poly")
class

class of object to return, spatial ("sp"), simple feature ("sf"), or data.frame ("df")
lon

range of longitude
lat

range of latitude

Value

Returns object with MERRA-2 grid information

Examples

getGrid()
